'''Taɣazut''' tga yat tiɣrmt mzziyn ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]] ifuss tmazirt n [[Amṛṛuk|Lmṛṛuk]] taggug s 20 km f tiɣrmt n [[Agadir|Ugadir]] d 153 km f tiɣrmt n [[Taṣṣurt]]. Ttuysan s taɣarin ns baḥra cwanin d iftasn zuzwanin.

Ar-d sis tackan imallayn ɣ graygat tamazirt n umaḍal. Midden ɣ tiɣrmt ad ddrn s tagmrt n [[islman]], d tiwuriwin n [[Tamallayt|tmallayt]] wala tiwuriwin n wakal tiyuga.

Aftas n twazut ar gis tmunan kraygat ungmar. Ilint ukan sul gis tiɣrubansn d imas n tuwuriwintnsn.
== Amzruy==
[[Afaylu:Buyirdn.jpg|thumb|Ixulan n Buyirdn]]
Tka-tt-in '''Taɣazut''' ɣ umruy nns lli nssn tga bdda yan udɣar lli f tmaɣen tiqbilin timaziɣin n zikk d ibraniyn. Ɣ tasut tiss 16, Ismun Mḥnd n Idir ɣ ṭṭerf nns tiqbilin, yumẓ lḥukm n tasga tagafayt n Taɣazut, izza ɣakud-ann f Ibrtqqiziyn. Willi mutn mḍeln-tn ɣ yan udɣar ɣ [[Tamraɣt]] iiga s ism Imuran. Macc ɣ ixf n tasut tiss 19, Isbnyuliyn umẓn Timzguida n Allal, gan as s ism " la madrague ", bnan gis luzinat, tigmma d yan uftas amaynu n tgmrt d immskaln n isɣnzitn. Ur sul iga ɣayan abla ixulan, ar asn tinin Ixulan n la madrague. Amma ɣila ḥiden ɣayam kullu.

Ɣ isggassn gr 1960 d 1970, Lkmn tisutin n ma mu tinin " hippies " s '''Taɣazut''' , nttni ad yujjan adɣar i iɛrrimn imɣrabiyn d willi skarn surf.

